    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The action or practice of ascending in balloons, which are flexible spherical bags made of a lightweight material inflated with heated air or a gas that is lighter than air. It is both a recreational activity and competitive sport. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
